Package: totallia
Title: Totallia: A Microbial Scale Repository for Paired Microbiome
 Sequence Count Data with Total Abundance Measurements
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
 person("Maxwell", "Konnaris",
        email = "mak6930@psu.edu",
        role  = c("aut", "cre")),
 person("Justin",  "Silverman",
        email = "JustinSilverman@psu.edu",
        role  = c("aut", "ctb"))
Maintainer: Maxwell Konnaris <mak6930@psu.edu>
Description: This R package parses and formats individual studies
 containing sequence count data and measurements of total abundance
 (Flow cytometry, ddPCR, qPCR, etc.) and returns a single data object
 containing any selected studies.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/Silverman-Lab/totallia
